snippet.title: The Turgenev Study - Harvest DNA and assimilate new samples for your research! 🦠
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://punkcake.itch.io/turgenev?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Harvest DNA and assimilate new samples for your paramountly important research. Your laboratory is located in a warzone, resulting in limited access to energy sources. Your agent can only launch a harvest every 10 seconds. Do your best despite theses harsh conditions.
